name: Qr04_Prop_Ourocap_N_Pag_Trata_Nao_Importune_NeoBpo - tel3
queryText:
SELECT
	A.CPF_CNPJ AS ID,
	CASE WHEN (A.CAMPANHA_NAO_IMPORTUNE = 1 AND N3.TELEFONE IS NOT NULL) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS NAO_IMPORTUNE
FROM Tb_Base_Prop_Ourocap_N_Pag A
LEFT JOIN TB_BASE_NAO_IMPORTUNE N3 ON ISNULL(CONCAT(A.DDD_TEL_03, A.TEL_03), '00000000000') = LTRIM(RTRIM(N3.TELEFONE))
